  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“On this shattered Earth of 2124, nothing is as it seems, but out on the track the truth is laid bare…”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELCOME TO THE NEON APEX</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earth, 2124. The cities have cracked. The machines have risen. But on the streets, one truth still burns: only the best survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Neon Apex is a high-speed arcade racer set in a world where humanity’s finest face off against AI-driven androids and cyber-enhanced challengers. Push your reflexes to the edge, hit every drift, and fight for glory at 200mph.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/2999c89cd1611815418e132991cd453b.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/2999c89cd1611815418e132991cd453b.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR RIDE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from a lineup of cars and bikes built for speed and style. Spend your winnings in the garage to boost performance, customize your setup, and stay ahead of the curve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/ca8a79f05ddc2b131727d551023c4441.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/ca8a79f05ddc2b131727d551023c4441.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEEL THE SPEED</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dominate the track in multiple game modes as you balance tight turns, traffic dodges, and tactical boost management. Every race is a test of nerve and control. One slip, and it’s over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/beb0e4e64d1139cdac23893dba71735c.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/beb0e4e64d1139cdac23893dba71735c.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LOOKS THAT KILL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With synth-heavy beats, neon-lit skylines, and stylized visuals inspired by ‘80s arcades, Neon Apex brings retro futurism to life with a modern twist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/3bf0da1237f79e401a82578b6b142ae8.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/3bf0da1237f79e401a82578b6b142ae8.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHASE LEGEND STATUS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete on global leaderboards to carve out your name at the top. You’ll either win or wipe out, so stay sharp and don’t blink.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“On this shattered Earth of 2124, nothing is as it seems, but out on the track the truth is laid bare…”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELCOME TO THE NEON APEX</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earth, 2124. The cities have cracked. The machines have risen. But on the streets, one truth still burns: only the best survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Neon Apex is a high-speed arcade racer set in a world where humanity’s finest face off against AI-driven androids and cyber-enhanced challengers. Push your reflexes to the edge, hit every drift, and fight for glory at 200mph.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/2999c89cd1611815418e132991cd453b.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/2999c89cd1611815418e132991cd453b.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR RIDE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from a lineup of cars and bikes built for speed and style. Spend your winnings in the garage to boost performance, customize your setup, and stay ahead of the curve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/ca8a79f05ddc2b131727d551023c4441.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/ca8a79f05ddc2b131727d551023c4441.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEEL THE SPEED</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dominate the track in multiple game modes as you balance tight turns, traffic dodges, and tactical boost management. Every race is a test of nerve and control. One slip, and it’s over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/beb0e4e64d1139cdac23893dba71735c.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/beb0e4e64d1139cdac23893dba71735c.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LOOKS THAT KILL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With synth-heavy beats, neon-lit skylines, and stylized visuals inspired by ‘80s arcades, Neon Apex brings retro futurism to life with a modern twist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/3bf0da1237f79e401a82578b6b142ae8.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/3bf0da1237f79e401a82578b6b142ae8.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHASE LEGEND STATUS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete on global leaderboards to carve out your name at the top. You’ll either win or wipe out, so stay sharp and don’t blink.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
